What is devChat?
=====
devChat is an open source IRC client for the UNIX terminal. It is intended to be very lightweight and easy to use while not sacrificing on features. It is under development.

Forking
=====
Please feel free to fork the repo to add anything you want or fix any bugs you've spotted. I'd also very much appreciate if you could send a pull request to fix it my sources as well.

